dct_title_s: Denmark Strait, Greenland (Denmark)-east coast, Griffenfeld Ø to Lemon Bugt (Raster Image)
dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. "From various sources to 1974." "LORAN-C." "Soundings in meters." Depths shown by soundings. Relief shown by contours, hachures, and spot heights. Includes compilation diagram. Title at right foot of chart: Griffenfeld Ø to Lemon Bugt. Map NO.38080.
This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
